  "description": "A panoramic view of a sandy beach curving along the coastline. The beach is bordered by grassy dunes on one side and the blue ocean on the other. Gentle waves roll onto the shore, creating white foam. In the background, a rolling hill covered in vegetation provides a backdrop, slightly obscured by a hazy atmosphere. A path or road can be seen winding through the dunes, with a few tiny figures of people scattered along the beach. The overall scene is tranquil and expansive, showcasing a natural coastal landscape.",
